snippet.title: Cheeky Chooks Seasons Update Trailer
snippet.description:
The Cheeky Chooks Season Update is here! Take on the new Adventure Mode and combat the elements across the changing seasons and weather. Complete all new missions and unlock new items and buildings and over 40 NEW Chooks and the arrival of LEGENDARY CHOOKS!
Ready to get Chooking?
